00:43:19.250 --> 00:43:20.840
when I was at TED.

00:43:20.840 --> 00:43:24.510
But when I was at TED, there was
this kind of lady who runs

00:43:24.510 --> 00:43:27.690
DARPA, and she kind of
released her killer

00:43:27.690 --> 00:43:30.360
hummingbird.

00:43:30.360 --> 00:43:32.440
And everyone was kind of wowed,
and then they're, oh my

00:43:32.440 --> 00:43:34.900
God, this hummingbird
can just kill.

00:43:34.900 --> 00:43:37.170
And now she's a bigwig
at Google.

00:43:37.170 --> 00:43:38.990
[LAUGHTER]

